19namespace ZXing {
20
21enum class CharacterSet;
22
23/**
24* Encapsulates a Character Set ECI, according to "Extended Channel Interpretations" 5.3.1.1
25* of ISO 18004.
26*
27* @author Sean Owen
28*/
29class CharacterSetECI
30{
31public:
32 /**
33 * @param value character set ECI value
34 * @return {@code CharacterSetECI} representing ECI of given value, or null if it is legal but
35 * unsupported
36 * @throws FormatException if ECI value is invalid
37 */
38 static CharacterSet CharsetFromValue(int value);
39
40 static int ValueForCharset(CharacterSet charset);
41
42 /**
43 * @param name character set ECI encoding name
44 * @return CharacterSetECI representing ECI for character encoding, or null if it is legal
45 * but unsupported
46 */
47 static CharacterSet CharsetFromName(const char* name);
48};
49
50} // ZXing
